::=====================================================================
::  [ CONFIGURE SYSTEM ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES FOR GEM PRODUCTS ]
::=====================================================================
::  SCRIPT INSTRUCTIONS:
::---------------------------------------------------------------------
::  TO TEST FOR EXISTING GEM ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES:
::.........................................................
::  1. Comment 'goto scriptSETX' ( e.g. ::goto scriptSETX )
::      --  This will run the echoEnvVar script block and
::      --  skip the scriptSETX block.
::
::      --  This script block will test if GEM Environment
::      --  Variables already exist. If they dont, goto step 2.
::
::  TO CONFIGURE NEW GEM ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES:
::.........................................................
::  2.  Uncomment '::goto scriptSETX' ( e.g. goto scriptSETX )
::      --  This will skip the echoEnvVar script block and
::      --  run the scriptSETX block.
::
::      --  This script block will configure System Environment
::      --  Variables with the listed GEM paths.
::      --  After running 'scriptSETX', run step 1 again to verify
::      --  that new GEM Environment Variables work correctly.
::=====================================================================
::+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++


::=====================================================================
::      [     ****  MODIFY THIS SECTION ONLY    ****        ]
::=====================================================================
::  To skip 'echoEnvVar' and run 'scriptSETX',
::  uncomment the following goto:
::.........................................................
::goto scriptSETX
::
::=====================================================================
::+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++


::=====================================================================
::      [     ----------- BEGIN SCRIPT  ------------        ]
::=====================================================================
::      [     ****  DO NOT MODIFY SCRIPT BLOCK  ****        ]
::=====================================================================
::
::.........................................................
::  echoEnvVar Script block
::.........................................................
:echoEnvVar
::---------------------------------------------------------
echo %GEM%
echo %GEM_IEX%
echo %GEM_ARC%
echo %GEM_AIMP%
echo %GEM_BFILES%
echo
::---------------------------------------------------------
goto done
::.........................................................
::  /echoEnvVar Script Block
::.........................................................
::
::=====================================================================
::+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++


::=====================================================================
::      [     ****  DO NOT MODIFY SCRIPT BLOCK      ****    ]
::=====================================================================
::
::.........................................................
::  scriptSETX Script block
::.........................................................
:scriptSETX
::---------------------------------------------------------------
setx GEM %~dp0
setx GEM_IEX %~dp0ImportExport\
setx GEM_ARC %~dp0ImportExport\Archive\
setx GEM_AIMP %~dp0ImportExport\Archive\ImportEmployees\
setx GEM_BFILES %~dp0ImportExport\Archive\ImportEmployees\BadFiles\
::---------------------------------------------------------------
goto done
::.........................................................
::  /scriptSETX Script Block
::.........................................................
::
::=====================================================================
::+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

:done

pause
